## Indicators (fresh data on {{timeframe}})

### Momentum & trend
- RSI (14): `{{indicators.rsi}}` (extreme < 30 or > 70; mid-range = neutral)
- EMA stack: 20=`{{indicators.ema20}}` / 50=`{{indicators.ema50}}` / 200=`{{indicators.ema200}}` — alignment = trend regime
- MACD: macd=`{{indicators.macd}}` signal=`{{indicators.macdSignal}}` hist=`{{indicators.macdHist}}` (hist sign change = momentum shift)

### Volatility regime (per-asset calibrated, not magic-number thresholds)
- ATR (14): `{{indicators.atr}}` | ATR z-score (200p): `{{indicators.atrZScore200}}` (< -1 compression, > +1.5 exhaustion territory — but in trending regimes high ATR = continuation, not reversal)
- BB bandwidth: `{{indicators.bbBandwidthPct}}%`, **percentile vs last 200 candles: `{{indicators.bbBandwidthPercentile200}}`** (< 15 = squeeze for THIS asset; the % itself is asset-dependent)

### Volume (pattern-conditional — see matrix below)
- Last/MA20: `{{indicators.lastVolume}}` / `{{indicators.volumeMa20}}` | **percentile (200p): `{{indicators.volumePercentile200}}`** (> 80 = spike for this asset, < 20 = anemic)

### Structure & liquidity
- Recent High / Low (50p): `{{indicators.recentHigh}}` / `{{indicators.recentLow}}`
- Last swing high: `{{indicators.lastSwingHigh}}` ({{indicators.lastSwingHighAge}} candles ago)
- Last swing low: `{{indicators.lastSwingLow}}` ({{indicators.lastSwingLowAge}} candles ago)
- **BOS state**: `{{indicators.bosState}}` (bullish/bearish = last structural break, 'none' = ranging)
- POC (point of control, last 50p): `{{indicators.pocPrice}}` — magnet / mean-reversion anchor (a setup with price stretched ≥1.5 ATR away from POC = mean-reversion candidate; near POC = compression / accumulation context)
- **Liquidity pools** (top equal-pivot clusters; high-touch = strong pool):
  - Above:{{#each indicators.topEqualHighs}} `{{this.price}}` ×{{this.touches}}{{/each}}{{#unless indicators.topEqualHighs.length}} (none){{/unless}}
  - Below:{{#each indicators.topEqualLows}} `{{this.price}}` ×{{this.touches}}{{/each}}{{#unless indicators.topEqualLows.length}} (none){{/unless}}

  Use these as concrete sweep targets / invalidation anchors in your proposals.

### VWAP
- Session VWAP: `{{indicators.vwapSession}}`, **price vs VWAP: `{{indicators.priceVsVwapPct}}%`**
  (above = institutional bias long; far above = stretched / mean-reversion candidate)

